Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.37,0:01:13.96,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}しばらくこのまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:18.45,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}理解不能　プログラム暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.61,0:01:21.27,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}原因は？
